      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This car is currently in poor condition, making it the absolute perfect candidate for a full restoration or a dedicated parts donor. If you're looking for a rewarding hands-on challenge to bring a vehicle back to life, this is the opportunity you've been waiting for!",
